WEBVTT

00:00.956 --> 00:02.996
It's over, Lorenzo!
The House of Medici falls today!

00:04.116 --> 00:05.250
Lorenzo must be found.

00:05.544 --> 00:07.579
He fled with the help
of the artista Da Vinci.

00:07.613 --> 00:09.280
Then he's alive.

00:09.315 --> 00:11.316
Lorenzo's lost blood,
he needs blood.

00:11.350 --> 00:13.184
I'll give him some of mine.

00:13.219 --> 00:15.653
Know what will happen if
the Pazzis enter these walls?

00:15.688 --> 00:17.789
Death to the Medicis!

00:19.225 --> 00:22.827
Count Riario abandoned you to
pursue some mysterious book.

00:22.862 --> 00:25.029
Where is Da Vinci?
Boarding a ship.

00:25.064 --> 00:27.198
Tell me the name
of the ship.

00:27.233 --> 00:28.466
The Basilisk.

00:28.501 --> 00:30.335
<i>If Da Vinci reaches</i>
<i>the Vault of Heaven,</i>

00:30.369 --> 00:32.070
<i>the Book Of Leaves</i>
<i>is his to claim.</i>

00:32.104 --> 00:33.738
Leonardo will
come for you.

00:33.772 --> 00:36.140
Tragically not for you.

00:36.175 --> 00:38.643
You have failed us,
Da Vinci.

00:38.677 --> 00:42.580
<i>Because of you, the Book Of</i>
<i>Leaves will be lost forever.</i>

00:42.615 --> 00:45.350
Stay back!

00:47.953 --> 00:51.953
<font color=#00FF00>♪ DaVinci's Demons 2x02 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Blood of Brothers</font>
