00:52.078 --> 00:56.977
== sync, corrected by <font color=#00FF00>elderman</font> ==
<font color=#00FFFF>@elder_man</font>

00:56.978 --> 01:50.966
♪

01:53.052 --> 01:54.052
What have you done to me?

01:54.086 --> 01:56.721
We cut open your veins
and my arteries

01:56.755 --> 01:58.089
and created a vacuum,

01:58.123 --> 02:01.192
which allowed my own blood
to replenish yours.

02:01.226 --> 02:03.795
Do you mean to say your blood
flows within me?

02:03.829 --> 02:05.730
I realize I'm not your
ideal candidate for blood brother,

02:05.764 --> 02:06.898
but the procedure
was too dangerous

02:06.932 --> 02:08.699
I couldn't
let anyone risk it.

02:12.605 --> 02:14.706
Where is Guiliano?

02:16.976 --> 02:18.910
Stay calm.

02:18.944 --> 02:21.613
As our attempt to save you will
be at risk if you don't.

02:21.647 --> 02:25.683
I wasn't asking you, maestro!
I was speaking to him!

02:25.718 --> 02:28.186
You've been through much,
Magnifico. Please.

02:28.220 --> 02:30.688
Put down the knife.
Where is my brother?

02:32.057 --> 02:34.792
By your allegiance,
Verrocchio, tell me now!

02:34.827 --> 02:39.897
Noble Giuliano
fought bravely.

02:39.932 --> 02:43.101
But was slain.

02:44.303 --> 02:46.971
I'm sorry, my lord.

